She smirked glancing to the side at Hydras. 

In her head she formed up a pattern of a defensive line. A line of Preds side 
by side.. to force a ton of firepower upon them. & advance upon them to 
weaken them as well. She'd seen this many times in previous battles in history, 
both organic, silicon & cybernetic. These usually worked.. otherwise, sometimes 
guerilla warfare working during other occassions. Her mind raced with what to 
do. 

Her optics glanced about to see what they could use at their advantage as 
well. 

"Predacons! Form a front line! Side by side!" pausing a moment. "I need 2 
with heavy firepower & can fly.... behind us & be reserve until I say!" 

She glanced over. "Who is our heavy artillery?!" 

--part1_168.20f70b87.2c34cee8_boundary
